title: The X Factor Australia 2015: UK singer Jess Glynne and axed Jimmy Davis look strikingly similar
text:
IT MAY just be the curly red hair but fans would be forgiven if they found themselves doing a second take during The X Factor last night.
UK singer Jess Glynne, who performed on the Channel 7 series, and recently axed Jimmy Davis looked strikingly similar.
CHAT TO THE AXED X FACTOR STARS FROM 2PM TODAY VIA FACEBOOK
UK Pop singer Jess Glynne. Picture: Mark Evans Jimmy Davis. Picture: Christian Gilles “Thank you for having me,” Glynne wrote after her appearance.
The 25-year-old holds the joint record alongside Cheryl Cole as the only British female artist to have five number one singles and recently topped the UK charts with her debut album, I Cry When I Laugh.
X Factor’s Jimmy Davis “It is such an amazing position to be in,” Glynne said.

An Australian tour is in the works for next year and is already thinking about her next album.
